title: Fishing-shooting-arcade games

creator: fishingstar
descriptionHtml:
The new era of 2023 is a popular fishing game for all people around the world, which originated from the perfect transplantation of classic fishing masters!
High explosive rate, fast winning points, thousands of cannonballs, making money every day, becoming a rich man every day!
Multiplayer online, real-life competition, big fish and small fish, catch all in one catch, the master of fishing is coming!
You can get a lot of free gold coins every day, and there are also mysterious props that are constantly being sent!
Don't miss it if you like large-scale machine games in the entertainment city!
I hope you can enjoy fishing in our video game city and experience the fun of crazy fishing!

【Game Features】
1. A large number of diamonds drop, quickly open thousands of cannons, feel the fun of the great god
2. Unique card draw function, get a large number of props, more worry-free than Polk recharge
3. Unique market function, get props to trade freely on the shelves, and experience the fun of merchants
4. Unique blessing function, hit a large number of gold coins, and go to the top of the fishing battle
5. Warheads are given away freely, without any conditions attached, and there are no bound props. Crazy Fishing is here
6. Brand-new guild gameplay, players in the whole server can socialize unlimitedly, fishing is no longer a game for one person
7.4 people on the same screen, add friends, chat freely, fishing is no longer lonely, and the palms are warm
8. 50000 times to open the special ability blessing of "charged cannon", making fishing more efficient, quickly sweeping away the fish on the screen, and experiencing the unparalleled feeling of mowing the grass.

【game introduction】
★ One of the most popular arcade fishing legends in Asian arcade halls. On the basis of the existing arcade fishing games, it fully realizes multiplayer online battles and making friends. Choice!
★ In the game, 4 people can play together in the same room, browse each other's avatar photos, send messages and chat in real time, see the fishing effect of friends in real time, and catch bosses together. The MMs in the game are really beautiful! GG is also so handsome! Make friends in the game and make friends!
★ In addition to the classic fishing gameplay, there are also various functions such as locking the fixed screen, with various beautiful and dazzling forts, the BOSS is crying with tears! If you catch the boss, you can drop a variety of props and treasure boxes, and there is also a lucky draw for pirate sharks. If you are a master-level fishing expert, you must remember to come and play, and the gods of the house will shout for you!
★ Different from other games, we will give away a lot of free gold coins, even if you don't store value, you can play every day and send them every day!
★ Finally, don't forget to bring your best friends with you to join the fantastic fishing adventure together!
※This software is classified as tutoring level 18+ according to the game software classification management method
※ Pay attention to the usage time and avoid indulging in the game
※The game does not offer "cash transaction gambling", and there is no chance to win cash or physical prizes.
※The practice status or achievements in social games do not mean that you will be successful in "cash transaction gambling" in the future.
